<function>

access:   public

name: image

param: string|Solar_Uri_Public, $src

param: array, $attribs, array ()

return: string

</function>

Returns an <img ... /> tag.

* Parameters:

 * string|Solar_Uri_Public //$src//: The href to the image source.

 * array //$attribs//: Additional attributes for the tag.

* Returns string: An <img ... /> tag.

Returns an <img ... /> tag.

If an "alt" attribute is not specified, will add it from the
image [[php basename()]].